&lt;p>知之者不如好之者，好之者不如乐之者。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>拥抱交易的学习曲线</title><link>/zh-hans/journey/post-04/</link><pubDate>Fri, 03 Oct 2025 00:01:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/zh-hans/journey/post-04/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>不怨天，不尤人，下学而上达。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>交易者必须了解的五大资产类别</title><link>/zh-hans/journey/post-05/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Oct 2025 00:01:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/zh-hans/journey/post-05/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>博学之，审问之，慎思之，明辨之，笃行之。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>交易与投资的四大学派（哪一种最适合你？）</title><link>/zh-hans/journey/post-06/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Oct 2025 00:01:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/zh-hans/journey/post-06/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
